524
00:18:31,485 --> 00:18:35,155
<i>Sir. Reporting from the operating room.</i>

525
00:18:33,445 --> 00:18:34,696
จากห้องผ่าตัดครับ

526
00:18:35,239 --> 00:18:36,615
How did it go?

527
00:18:35,239 --> 00:18:36,615
